  "description": {
    "zh": "Terragroup 实验室，一个极其危险却充满宝藏的地方。这里经常被人搜刮和占领，到处都是装备精良的 PMC 和 Raider。\n\n我需要你清理一下这个地方，我可以为你提供一些访问卡。当然，顺便带走所有有价值的物品，也许对你、我或者我们都有用。准备好了吗？",
    "en": "The Terragroup Laboratory, extremely dangerous but filled with treasure. That place gets raided constantly, a lot of geared locals and former PMCs.\n\nI want you to clean up the place a bit, I can supply you with a few access cards for that. Oh and by the way, take whatever valuable shit you find with you. It might be of use for you, me or both of us."
  },
